    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<style> .bor{border:1px dashed #F00;width:300px;min-height:10px;margin-top:10px} /*span{display:block}让span形成块*/ </style> <center><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mjx-dev/assets@master/website/img/blog/3-cover.jpg" width="800px" alt="cover"></center><h2 id="jquery安装"><a href="#jquery安装" class="headerlink" title="jquery安装"></a>jquery安装</h2><p>再使用jquery前,先要提及一下jquery的安装(大佬跳过)<br>主要分为两种类型,本地安装与云端(cdn)引用</p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="本地安装"><a href="#本地安装" class="headerlink" title="本地安装"></a>本地安装</h3><p>可以去<a href="https://jquery.com/download/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">jquery官网</a>下载相关文件<br>文件分为两种类型:</p><ul><li>Production version (用于实际应用,代码压缩)</li><li>Development version (用于开发和测试,代码可读)</li></ul><p>下载下来可以放到js目录中</p><p>使用时把以下代码放到<b style="color:red">head标签</b>内</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"jquery-1.10.2.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="云端引用"><a href="#云端引用" class="headerlink" title="云端引用"></a>云端引用</h3><p>大家也可以引用云上的文件,选一个CDN,并把代码放到<b style="color:red">head标签</b>内<br>官方 CDN:</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"http://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.1.1.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Staticfile CDN:</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://cdn.staticfile.org/jquery/1.10.2/jquery.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>百度 CDN:</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/2.1.4/jquery.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>又拍云 CDN:</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://upcdn.b0.upaiyun.com/libs/jquery/jquery-2.0.2.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>新浪 CDN</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://lib.sinaapp.com/js/jquery/2.0.2/jquery-2.0.2.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Google CDN(国内不稳定)</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.10.2/jquery.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Microsoft CDN</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://ajax.aspnetcdn.com/ajax/jquery/jquery-1.9.0.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>mjx(本站) CDN(乱入?→详见资源站)</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/mjx-dev/assets@master/website/res/jquery-2.1.1.min.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="隐藏-显示"><a href="#隐藏-显示" class="headerlink" title="隐藏/显示"></a>隐藏/显示</h2><p>语法:</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$(selector).hide(speed,callback);</span><br><span class="line">$(selector).show(speed,callback);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>selector可以为:</p><ul><li>“#id”(控件id)</li><li>“label”(标签名)</li></ul><p>speed可以取三种类型:</p><ul><li>“slow”</li><li>“fast”</li><li>数字(ms)</li></ul><p>callback为一个函数<br>示例jquery:(放入script标签)</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$(<span class="string">"#hide"</span>).click(<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  $(<span class="string">"p"</span>).hide();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">$(<span class="string">"#show"</span>).click(<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  $(<span class="string">"p"</span>).show();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>示例html:(放入body标签)</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>如果你点击“隐藏” 按钮，我将会消失。<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">button</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">"hide"</span>&gt;</span>隐藏<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">button</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">button</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">"show"</span>&gt;</span>显示<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">button</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>示例↓↓↓↓</p><script src="https://apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/2.1.4/jquery.min.js"></script><div class="bor"><p id="widget">如果你点击“隐藏” 按钮，我将会消失。</p><button id="hide">隐藏</button><button id="show">显示</button></div><script>$("#hide").click(function(){  $("#widget").hide();});$("#show").click(function(){  $("#widget").show();});</script>]]></content>
    
